 =?UTF-8?q?=20board,=20fase-filter,=20auto-pages,=20AlertModalCore?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Six improvements built on the v2 native integration:

1. AlertModalCore replaces all confirm() calls (phase-controls, phase-chip,
   vault page) — native Plane modals for advance/archive confirmations

2. Pipeline Board at /:workspaceSlug/pipeline — BaseKanbanLayout with one
   column per production phase, drag-drop between phases, clickable cards

3. Fase-filter pills on /projects page — client-side filter bar above the
   project grid; click any phase to filter, click again to clear

4. Auto-page creation on phase advance — each transition creates a best-effort
   template page (Design Sample 1/2/3, Pre-productie planning, etc.)

5. Vault cards now navigate to project on click; AlertModalCore for Start Design

6. RivettaPhaseBadge in pages list header (next to tab navigation)

New files:
  apps/web/app/(all)/[workspaceSlug]/(projects)/pipeline/page.tsx
  apps/web/core/components/rivetta/pipeline-board.tsx

